  <div id="aboutus" class="span4 red_title">
    <h3>About WeTheNation</h3>
    <p>WeTheNation is a non-partisan, not for profit, social site that provides the facts about Congress including its current members and current legislation. WeTheNation provides users a way to keep track of, vote on, and share their opinions on current members and bills in Congress. WeTheNation is your starting point for getting involved in politics and the issues important to you. Real change starts at the Congressional level, and its starts with you.</p>
    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>Our mission is simple; to make politics engaging, interesting, and fun. We know how difficult it can be to stay up to date on bills and members in the news and we hope to provide our users with a portal of information that is both factual and accurate. We encourage activism through education, knowledge is power and we want to empower all citizens to be as up-to-date on the issues as possible. United we can make a better tomorrow.</p>
  </div>
